hello all! You know that workspace-loading spinner weâ€™re all used to seeing for an eternity when you load the main workspace page for the first time? I just merged a change that should cut that time down drastically (for me it went down from > 16s to like 2s). But I had to change up the way some things were stored in Redis. So if anyone sees weird repo/acl-related errors when working locally, please make sure to delete your redis cache:
```cd <folder you run redis from>
rm dump.rdb```
